                    <pre><code>POST https://devalentineapi.onrender.app/api/partners/add</code></pre>
                    <pre><code>PUT https://devalentineapi.onrender.app/api/partners/update/{partnerId}</code></pre>
                    <pre><code>DELETE https://devalentineapi.onrender.app/api/partners/delete/{partnerId}</code></pre>

                    <h6>Testimonials</h6>
